<section>
<title>Description détaillée</title>

<para>HTTP Bearer authentication utility.</para>

<para>This class helps you setup bearer auth. The process is fairly simple:</para>

<para><orderedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Instantiate the class.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Call getToken (this will return null or a token as string)</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>If you didn&apos;t get a valid token, call &apos;requireLogin&apos;</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>

